    "title": "McDonald's India is Hiring: Guest Relations Manager (Lead)",
    "description": "McDonald's India is actively seeking a talented and motivated Guest Relations Manager to join our dynamic team in Tiruchirappalli. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout McDonald's India:\nMcDonald's India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with McDonald's India!",
